Detailed Description

cvmx_mix::_intena

MIX_INTENA = MIX Local Interrupt Enable Mask Register

Description: NOTE: To write to the MIX_INTENA register, a device would issue an IOBST directed at the MIO. To read the MIX_INTENA register, a device would issue an IOBLD64 directed at the MIO.
